data.description: One-level living with a spacious feel. Three nice-sized bedrooms make this home feel larger than it is. Great neighbors make this a great home for a family to start out or for empty-nesters who are downsizing. The cul-de-sac is quiet and the lot backs up to a lovely natural area with trees and a pond. Enjoy a morning cup of coffee on the screened in back porch where you can enjoy watching the wildlife. All this and the ease and conveniences of Helena just down the street.
data.whatILove: The home is located in the cul-de-sac and backs up to a lovely pond. We love the newly screened in back porch where we enjoy a cup of coffee or tea and watch the rabbits, deer, and birds around the pond. We also LOVE the neighbors.
